          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35993915/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35993915/" class="">第34页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/59640603/" class=" " title="妖精">妖精</a>
                (若是没有你，我苟延残喘)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="35993915">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">

盖历史的事实，自佛家观之，只是习气流转，互摄交融，成为业缘果报之总相。如由习气看历史，则历史本身非自由的，历史人物亦非自由的，此不自由之故，即为业力所驱使。


</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-08-28 09:34</span>
                  
                </p>
